	<description>Thanks for installing the intro_flv module v1.0 from Studiosacchetti. This module displays a video on loading page.  you can just ignore the unused parameters but they must be in sequence. Name your video whatever you like, and upload into the modules/mod_intro_flv/ folder. Lastly, be sure to set permissions to 777.
